we added "sput2" (energy sputtering yield), "sputchem", "sputchee",
"thermev", "thermeve", "sputres", "sputrese", "platemp" and "sheath",
which all work under the same principle of printing the desired quantity
in a user-specified input file, and where the other parameters (if any)
